```server-java
documentsDB.createDocuments(
  "<DATABASE_ID>",
  "<COLLECTION_ID>",
  Arrays.asList(
    Map.of(
      "$id", ID.unique(),
      "name", "One"
    ),
    Map.of(
      "$id", ID.unique(),
      "name", "Two"
    )
  ),
  "<TRANSACTION_ID>",
  new CoroutineCallback<>((result, error) -> {
    if (error != null) {
      error.printStackTrace();
      return null;
    }
    System.out.println(result);
    return null;
  })
);
```
```rust
